WILDCAT DRILLING, L.L.C.
v.
DISCOVERY OIL & GAS, L.L.C. 2019-0222 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 20, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSAL

Appellant has not filed a merit brief, due August 12, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
